	  list:

	  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonRDS/latest/UserGuide/Concepts.RegionsAndAvailabilityZones.html
	  https://gist.github.com/neilstuartcraig/0ccefcf0887f29b7f240

config TERRAFORM_AWS_AV_REGION_WEST_2B
